# Grocery Backend API

A production‑ready backend built with FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, and JWT authentication. This project includes core modules such as authentication, products, orders, cart, wishlist, and admin utilities.

---

## Features

- User Authentication (JWT based login/signup)
- Product Management (CRUD, categories, popularity filter)
- Order Management (create order, order status, coupon handling)
- Cart System (add/remove/update items)
- Wishlist System (add/remove items)
- Image Upload (via Form‑Data)
- Admin Utilities (sales report filters)
- SQLAlchemy ORM models with relationships
- Enum-based status fields for reliability
- Environment‑based config structure

---

